# ─── Contact form (Resend) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Get an API key at https://resend.com/api-keys
RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_api_key_here

# Inbox that receives contact-form messages.
# Defaults to the address in src/lib/site.ts if omitted.
CONTACT_TO=contact@sadabmunshi.online

# Verified sender — MUST be on a domain you've verified in Resend.
# Your verified domain is "sadabmunshi.online", so use an address on it:
CONTACT_FROM=Sadab Munshi Website <noreply@sadabmunshi.online>
#
# Notes:
#   • The "from" domain must EXACTLY match a verified domain in Resend.
#     A subdomain like "app.sadabmunshi.online" counts as a DIFFERENT domain
#     unless you verified that subdomain specifically.
#   • The mailbox (e.g. "noreply") does not need to exist as a real inbox.
#   • For quick testing only, Resend's shared sender works without a domain:
#       CONTACT_FROM=onboarding@resend.dev
